            <div class="ArticleImgContent">
                <h2>
                    <a href="/en/dep/ad/pressesenter/pressemeldinger/2009/retur-av-einslege-mindrearige-asylsokjar.html?id=575674" title="">
                        Return of unaccompanied minor asylum seekers
                    </a>
                </h2>
                <h3 class="subDescription" style="display:none"></h3>
                <p class="ArticleInfo">[Press release, Ministry of Labour, 04.09.2009]</p>
                <p>The Ministry of Labor and Social Inclusion changes the practice for return of unaccompanied minor asylum seekers. The changes makes it possible to return unaccompanied minors to relatives or other care measures in the home country. </p>
                
                
                <p>
                    
                    
                </p>
