                <img src="/upload/AID/temabilder/alle_temaer/tema_aid36_100x75.jpg" alt="Stronger demands on documented identity in asylum cases" class="ArticleImg" />
            </a>
            <div class="ArticleImgContent">
                <h2>
                    <a href="/en/dep/ad/pressesenter/pressemeldinger/2009/strengere-krav-til-dokumentert-identitet.html?id=565154" title="">
                        Stronger demands on documented identity in asylum cases
                    </a>
                </h2>
                <h3 class="subDescription" style="display:none"></h3>
                <p class="ArticleInfo">[Press release, Ministry of Labour, 08.06.2009]</p>
                <p>The Norwegian Directorate of Immigration (UDI) has received instructions to request stronger demands on documented identity in asylum cases. If an asylum seeker refuses to do what is practically possible to document his or her identity, then the authorities will, to a larger extent, deny or issue a limited permission.</p>
                
                
                <p>
                    
                    
                </p>
